Hello Monsta & Sam Rudi, welcome to Wudup Crib! enjoy and have great day!

Monsta & Sam Rudi are character designed by Rasuardie and currently hanging around on crypto through H=N. These character are quite familiar around 2000's era when the wave of independent comic arise in Indonesia.

Wudup Series in collaboration with Rasuardie

ABOUT WUDUP SERIES
Wudup is a series created by Artkelso (Ritchie Ned Hansel) presenting a repetition of his trademark character Mr. Chicken Bird. Here the series will be featured with guest stars that will appear on the right side of the artboards. Enjoy and don't have a good day, HAVE A GREAT DAY!
